"""
part3_processing.py
Part 3 pipeline: ensembles, tuning, and a reproducible sklearn Pipeline, built on
top of the exact same feature matrix and Spam/Ham classification target from Part 2.

Reuses load_cleaned() and build_features_and_labels() from part2_processing so the
feature set (12 leak-free columns) is identical across Parts 2 and 3 -- required for
the Task 8 summary comparison table to be a fair apples-to-apples comparison.

NOTE ON RUNTIME: Task 6 (GridSearchCV, 18 configs x 5 folds = 90 RandomForest fits)
and Task 6b (5 more pipeline fits for the learning curve) make this the slowest
pipeline in the app -- expect ~1-3 minutes per run, depending on host CPU. This is
inherent to the assignment spec (exhaustive grid search), not an inefficiency here.
"""
